{"database_schema": ""Description for table: Artist"
type Artist @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the artist"
  id: ID!
  "Blockchain address associated with the artist"
  address: Bytes!
  "Name of the artist"
  name: String
  "Total number of editions created by the artist"

  ccEditionsCount: BigInt!
  "Total supply of artworks by the artist"
  supply: BigInt!
  "Total number of artworks issued by the artist"
  issuedCount: BigInt!
  "Total value of the artist's sales in Ethereum"
  totalValueInEth: BigDecimal!
  "Total number of sales made by the artist"
  salesCount: BigInt!
  "Total primary sales made by the artist"
  totalPrimarySales: BigInt!
  "Total primary sales value in Ethereum"
  totalPrimarySalesInEth: BigDecimal!
  "Total secondary sales made by the artist"
  totalSecondarySales: BigInt!
  "Total secondary sales value in Ethereum"
  totalSecondarySalesInEth: BigDecimal!
  "Highest sale value achieved by the artist in Ethereum"
  highestSaleValueInEth: BigDecimal!
  "Token associated with the highest sale"
  highestSaleToken: Token
  "First edition created by the artist"
  firstEdition: Edition
  "Timestamp of the first edition created"
  firstEditionTimestamp: BigInt!
  "Most recent edition created by the artist"
  lastEdition: Edition
  "Timestamp of the most recent edition created"
  lastEditionTimestamp: BigInt!
  "List of editions created by the artist"
  editions: [Edition!]! @derivedFrom(field: "artist")

  editionIds: [Edition!]!
  "Configuration for minting by the artist"
  mintingConfig: ArtistMintingConfig!
  "Contracts created by the artist"
  creatorContracts: [CreatorContract!]
}"}
